JOHANNESBURG - In this cracking episode of The Clinch TV, Simon Stephens is joined in studio by former UFC fighter Gareth ‘Soldier Boy’ Mclellan to discuss his unexpected farewell from the Ultimate Fighting Championship. Mclellan, who fought in the US for two-and-a-half years, has insisted that he looks forward to joining the South African MMA industry again. *Watch the full interview in the gallery above or listen and download The Clinch TV's full episode below. eNCA